WEBVTT

26:36.200 --> 26:37.240 line:80%
Who are you?

26:37.350 --> 26:39.430 line:80%
Trying to deny it?

26:39.450 --> 26:41.680 line:80%
We were drinking at the tavern

26:41.720 --> 26:43.370 line:80%
when you approached us.

26:43.400 --> 26:44.200 line:80%
You're still trying to deny it?

26:44.200 --> 26:44.910 line:80%
Exactly.

26:45.000 --> 26:46.630 line:80%
The tavern owner can testify too.
